The Sages call it the living fire, because God has endowed it with His
own Divine, and vitalising power. ... No student of this Art can possibly
do without it. For another Sage says： ‘In this invisible fire you have
the whole mystery of this Art, as the three Persons of the Holy Trinity are
truly concluded in one substance."
